{"tid":1385990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(追夢) 社區環保收集　轉贈有需要的香港人   團結一致　有錢出錢　有力出力　","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:24:39.000Z","uid":103728,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"779332869876af043daa59cc571c3d253af8c6b7","tid":1385990,"uid":103728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chiuchupong/posts/2248363268827763?__xts__[0]=68.ARD57LcpEdufIe24xmKfOeTlDMGyEvM1mXahftQsCX57xKNzYiyFa6kSL_D0ataGLBHlJZpgjHRICDDQrQeoI7hr3KD0ns2t5X3EAurQ_QEn92gy6tp6DgAviFRPRGbseqvqfO2xLdak9ypZ1f1juCOX22NmJbG13SRwbmytfdxA9j_rfzQQP0EuKFCaXyg94G-Ha-FvWaJre8uVeBAn_HKJx5AWlq0T00QhnDtjeTUSE31KXFnfhfP_QoNcp2tr7LKMg84QVFexiuYngS-PAKCa_1eWeBDpFhFO8pQdTTAfwl_WeKSM2lGLinVYUP7J_o2XxLLUzgxEQT7-0flwySMHOVxt&amp;__tn__=-R[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchiuchupong%2Fposts%2F2248363268827763%3F__xts__%5B0%5D%3D68.ARD57LcpEdufIe24xmKfOeTlDMGyEvM1mXahftQsCX57xKNzYiyFa6kSL_D0ataGLBHlJZpgjHRICDDQrQeoI7hr3KD0ns2t5X3EAurQ_QEn92gy6tp6DgAviFRPRGbseqvqfO2xLdak9ypZ1f1juCOX22NmJbG13SRwbmytfdxA9j_rfzQQP0EuKFCaXyg94G-Ha-FvWaJre8uVeBAn_HKJx5AWlq0T00QhnDtjeTUSE31KXFnfhfP_QoNcp2tr7LKMg84QVFexiuYngS-PAKCa_1eWeBDpFhFO8pQdTTAfwl_WeKSM2lGLinVYUP7J_o2XxLLUzgxEQT7-0flwySMHOVxt%26__tn__%3D-R%5B%2Furl%5D&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=9ea1475d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chiuchupong/posts/2248363268827763?__xts__[0]=68.ARD57LcpEdufIe24xmKfOeTlDMGyEvM1mXahftQsCX57xKNzYiyFa6kSL_D0ataGLBHlJZpgjHRICDDQrQeoI7hr3KD0ns2t5X3EAurQ_QEn92gy6tp6DgAviFRPRGbseqvqfO2xLdak9ypZ1f1juCOX22NmJbG13SRwbmytfdxA9j_rfzQQP0EuKFCaXyg94G-Ha-FvWaJre8uVeBAn_HKJx5AWlq0T00QhnDtjeTUSE31KXFnfhfP_QoNcp2tr7LKMg84QVFexiuYngS-PAKCa_1eWeBDpFhFO8pQdTTAfwl_WeKSM2lGLinVYUP7J_o2XxLLUzgxEQT7-0flwySMHOVxt&amp;__tn__=-R[/url]</a><br />\n社區環保收集 轉贈有需要的香港人<br />\n團結一致 有錢出錢 有力出力 <br />\n<br />\n回收物品：<br />\n舊衣(不同顏色運動衣服)、急救用品、保護防具（地盤開工口罩，保護自己，嚴防肺積塵）、現金券、用餐券、已增值八達通等等<br />\n<br />\n致香港的小孩、年青人、追夢者及愛心家長，幫主辦事處本著熱心及關心市民的責任，將全力收集任何一切協助年青人及追夢者的物資，本人以人格擔保，將一切物資必定轉贈到有需要的小孩及年青人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有人想食飯吹水訴心聲，黎博康邨或沙田，阿幫一定奉陪！<br />\n如果有年青人，特別是沙田柚，因為近月的社會運動，與家人出現紛爭、無家可歸、有經濟困難、好唔開心、心灰意冷、需要聆聽者，需要幫忙的話。幫主願意與大家同行，互相支持，請聯絡我，我幫到一定盡幫。<br />\n<br />\n總之應承我地，大家唔好死，留返條命迎接勝利！<br />\n前排經歷714，我都灰機左十日，但我知道呢場仗，我地要堅持到底，我地唔可以就咁放棄，一輸就輸哂所有。<br />\n<br />\n勸告各位愛香港的年青人，唔好再送頭比呢個政權，因為唔值得，為呢個暴政而放棄自由同生命，甚至於坐冤獄同死亡。<br />\n<br />\n求下大家留返條命，唔好死下係暴政暴警之下。（至於幫主是否可信，大家自行考慮。）<br />\n<br />\n幫主沙田博康邨議員辦事處聯絡：<br />\n博康辦：37099071<br />\n手機：63471955 <br />\n地址：博康邨博逸樓地下1號（歡迎郵寄）<br />\n門外：公民抗命信箱 (24小時收貨)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ne2Nipn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fne2Nipn.jpg&h=6538c3a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MXOQga2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMXOQga2.jpg&h=b47823e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umdMyXJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumdMyXJ.jpg&h=3fae4356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ectNhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ectNhK.jpg&h=f61043a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ak3gWa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAk3gWa4.jpg&h=6b3df5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cry8NhL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCry8NhL.jpg&h=807e7d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPqryXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPqryXM.jpg&h=8edf15eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHsxuv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHsxuv6.jpg&h=18cdf351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzwBWa6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=